OL,4,CFewer flat buyers to face pre-mortgage
OL,5,Ccladding checks, says Robert Jenrick
OL,6, People buying flats in buildings lower
OL,7, than 18m (59ft) in England will no
OL,8, longer have to provide safety details
OL,9, on external walls to get a mortgage,
OL,10, the government has said.
OL,12,FBarclays, HSBC and Lloyds welcomed the
OL,13,Fchange, and said it should pave the way
OL,14,Ffor updated industry guidance.
OL,16,FIt follows concerns over large bills to
OL,17,Fremove cladding facing many flat owners
OL,18,Fsince the Grenfell Tower fire.
OL,20,FBut Labour called the height-based
OL,21,Fstipulation "arbitrary".
